headline: With charger funding under threat, ChargePoint's Eaton deal is bet on a 'better product,' CEO says
summary: While President Trump and the House Republicans attempt to pull the plug on President Biden's EV charging funding, ChargePoint (CHPT) and industrial energy giant Eaton (ETN) are trying to keep the spark alive.
